cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is about human action recognition using convolutional neural networks (CNNs) with video input. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a novel convolution block for CNN architectures, which suggests it could be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
